OL,3,C'Deal reached' to sell Morecambe FC
OL,5,FA deal has been reached to sell
OL,6,Ftroubled football club Morecambe after
OL,7,Fmonths of turmoil and internal
OL,8,Farguments.
OL,10,FThe Shrimps, who were relegated from
OL,11,FLeague Two at the end of the 2024/25
OL,12,Fseason, were at risk of "immediate
OL,13,Fclosure" due to a financial crisis
OL,14,Fafter talks to buy the 105-year-old
OL,15,Fclub fell through a number of times.
OL,17,FThe club have been relegated twice in
OL,18,Fthe past three seasons and were
OL,19,Fofficially put up for sale in
OL,20,FSeptember 2022 by owners Bond Group.
