OL,3,C'Deal reached' to sell Morecambe FC
OL,5,FSports investment company Panjab
OL,6,FWarriors have been in talks to buy the
OL,7,Fclub from owner Jason Whittingham for
OL,8,Fmore than a year, with a deal looked
OL,9,Fset to be concluded earlier this
OL,10,Fsummer.
OL,12,FBut those talks stalled after
OL,13,FWhittingham said he was in discussions
OL,14,Fwith other potential investors and, as
OL,15,Ftensions escalated, each party issued
OL,16,Faccusatory statements about the other.
