OL,3,C'Deal reached' to sell Morecambe FC
OL,5,FNow however both parties say they are
OL,6,F"pleased to announced that an
OL,7,Fagreement has been reached in
OL,8,Fprinciple for the transfer of majority
OL,9,Fshareholding".
OL,11,FAnnouncing the deal, Whittingham's
OL,12,FBond Group Investments apologised "for
OL,13,Fthe stress...caused" and thanked the
OL,14,Fclub for its patience.
