OL,3,C'Deal reached' to sell Morecambe FC
OL,5,FA joint statement posted on the club's
OL,6,Fsite went on to add: "Following
OL,7,Fconstructive discussions and a shared
OL,8,Fcommitment to securing the future of
OL,9,Fthe club, both parties have agreed to
OL,10,Fa structured settlement that ensures a
OL,11,Fsmooth and fair transition.
OL,13,F"This agreement reflects the
OL,14,Fwillingness of both sides to
OL,15,Fcompromise in the best interests of
OL,16,FMorecambe FC, its supporters, and the
OL,17,Fwider community. It paves the way for
OL,18,Fcontinued stability and a positive
OL,19,Ffuture both on and off the pitch."
